				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "One of the plaque in the Central Square.\r\nYou need to click on the 3 plaques in a correct sequence to unlock a secret entrance to the secret room underneath the central square.\r\nThe correct sequence: 2-3-1\r\n\r\nThe plaques should either tell the history of Ketheric Thorm / this outpost or be some sort of propaganda."
